1. clone this repo to your machine.
2. Navigate to submission directory, create a directory with your name ex: vikas_practice and place all your answers in this directory.
  - write all commands you executed in commaands_executed.txt file with corresponding question.
  - take snippets of all executed commands and results and save it snippets directory with question number, create a snippets directory after step2 directory.
  - make sure to push all without missing.
3. download this rar file https://drive.google.com/file/d/1KQITJ7GSpf9iROxk7yfkoscaI4Ky3b-F/ into your machine and then start your linux questions.

__Provide answers for below questions in devops_answers.txt__

1. What is DevOps
2. What is Automation, Scaling, Infrastructure
3. Why DevOps is Important, etc
  
